Sandman Special rules: <br>
<br>
No Matter what the odds - Sandmen are stubborn, bitter, hardened fighters. They ignore the negative modifiers for being outnumbered in combat. <br>
<br>
“To the aid of my brethren!” – Sandmen are know for their ability to strike with righteous fervor for the aid of their follow Space Marines. To represent this All Sandmen strike with 2 attacks when assisting in combat. Note that they still do not gain the benefit of special weaponry and this does not mean they are striking with their full compliment of attacks. It simply augments their ability to support in combat.<br>
