<br>
Weapons: Bolters. The Sergeant may replace his bolter with a bolt pistol and close combat weapon for no additional cost or a storm bolter for +5pts. <br>
<br>
Options: One Space Marine in the squad may be armed with one of the following weapons: heavy bolter +5 pts; missile launcher +10 pts; lascannon +15 pts; flamer +6pts; meltagun +10 pts; plasma gun +6pts. <br>
<br>
In addition, if the squad numbers at least 8 in total then one Space Marine may also be armed with one of the following weapons: heavy bolter +15 pts; missile launcher +20 pts; lascannon +35 pts, multi-melta +35 pts, plasma cannon +35 pts. <br>
