Fast Attack <br>
<br>
Grey Death Assault Squad <br>
<br>
The Grey Death is renowned for using assault troops to take out enemy tanks. To represent this all Grey Death Assault Squads MUST purchase krak grenades for every member of the squad for +2 points per model or melta bombs for +4 points per model. <br>
<br>
Grey Death Assault Squads are also extremely well trained at the task of vehicle destruction and the ability to escape harm during the process. When rolling on the Penetrating hits result chart (not glancing), Grey Death Assault Squads add +1 to their roll. They also only suffer wounds on a 5+ in the event of explosion instead of the usual 4+. <br>
<br>
Land Speeder Squadron  <br>
<br>
If the Land Speeder Squadron numbers at least 2 models, one of the Land Speeders may be replaced by a Land Speeder Tornado or a Land Speeder Typhoon. Note Typhoons and Tornados cannot be included in a Grey Death army individually. <br>
